[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ilford shooting: Man found shot and stabbed in car

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been found shot and stabbed in a car East London.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Emergency services found the 22-year-old with "life changing" injuries inside the vehicle on High Road, Ilford, just before 05:00 GMT.
Detectives from Trident, the Met Police's specialist gang crime unit, are investigating. One man has been arrested on suspicion of affray.
A witness travelling past the scene described it as resembling a "war zone".
